# Copy this file to tradingview.secret (same folder) and paste your secret on line 1.
# Do not commit tradingview.secret - it is gitignored.
#
# Paste ONLY the secret value (one line), e.g.:
#   a1b2c3d4e5f6789012345678901234567890abcd
#
# Or use KEY=value form:
#   TRADINGVIEW_WEBHOOK_SECRET=your-secret-here
#
# TradingView Pine charts: set "Hermes webhook secret" to the same value.
#
# Webhook URL for TradingView alerts (expose port 8810 with ngrok first):
#   https://YOUR-NGROK-SUBDOMAIN.ngrok-free.app/webhooks/tradingview
#
# Local test (PowerShell) after Docker is up:
#   .\scripts\test-tradingview-webhook.ps1
#
PASTE_YOUR_SECRET_HERE
